<div style="background-color:#fcefdc; padding: 20px;">
    <h2 style="color:#822b2b;">Help:</h2>
    <p>Welcome to our help section!</p>
    <p>Here you can find answers to frequently asked questions and useful information about our services. If you can’t find what you’re looking for, feel free to contact us — we’re here for you! 🌸</p>

    <h4><a href="#">How can I order flowers?</a></h4>
    <p>It’s very easy! Choose the bouquet or arrangement you like, add it to your cart, enter your delivery details, and complete your order through our secure online platform.</p>

    <h4><a href="#">What are the payment options?</a></h4>
    <p>You can pay online via card or in cash upon delivery.</p>

    <h4><a href="#">Can I order anonymously?</a></h4>
    <p>Yes. If you want your order to be anonymous, just mention that in the order notes.</p>

    <h4><a href="#">Do you deliver outside the city?</a></h4>
    <p>We deliver in the city and nearby areas. For special requests or distant deliveries, please contact us before ordering.</p>
